        Poly-analytic functions AND representation theory
      
    </p>
    <p class="authors">
      <span class="has-text-black-bis has-text-weight-semibold">Authors:</span>
      
      <a href="/search/?searchtype=author&amp;query=Turbiner%2C+A+V">Alexander V Turbiner</a>, 
      
