    <p class="title is-5 mathjax">
      
        Division <span class="search-hit mathjax">algebras</span> and MRD codes from skew polynomials
      
    </p>
    <p class="authors">
      <span class="has-text-black-bis has-text-weight-semibold">Authors:</span>
      
      <a href="/search/?searchtype=author&amp;query=Thompson%2C+D">Daniel Thompson</a>, 
      
      <a href="/search/?searchtype=author&amp;query=Pumpluen%2C+S">Susanne Pumpluen</a>
      
