    <p class="title is-5 mathjax">
      
        Deciding Stability of Sheaves on Curves
      
    </p>
    <p class="authors">
      <span class="has-text-black-bis has-text-weight-semibold">Authors:</span>
      
      <a href="/search/?searchtype=author&amp;query=Brenner%2C+H">Holger Brenner</a>, 
      
      <a href="/search/?searchtype=author&amp;query=Steinbuch%2C+J">Jonathan Steinbuch</a>
      
