    <p class="title is-5 mathjax">
      
        Mirror symmetry for truncated cluster varieties
      
    </p>
    <p class="authors">
      <span class="has-text-black-bis has-text-weight-semibold">Authors:</span>
      
      <a href="/search/?searchtype=author&amp;query=Gammage%2C+B">Benjamin Gammage</a>, 
      
      <a href="/search/?searchtype=author&amp;query=Le%2C+I">Ian Le</a>
      
