    <p class="title is-5 mathjax">
      
        Gradings on the <span class="search-hit mathjax">algebra</span> of triangular matrices as a Lie <span class="search-hit mathjax">algebra</span>: revisited
      
    </p>
    <p class="authors">
      <span class="has-text-black-bis has-text-weight-semibold">Authors:</span>
      
      <a href="/search/?searchtype=author&amp;query=Koshlukov%2C+P">Plamen Koshlukov</a>, 
      
      <a href="/search/?searchtype=author&amp;query=Yasumura%2C+F+Y">Felipe Yukihide Yasumura</a>
      
