        Asymptotic stability of diffusion waves of a quasi-linear hyperbolic-parabolic model for vasculogenesis
      
    </p>
    <p class="authors">
      <span class="has-text-black-bis has-text-weight-semibold">Authors:</span>
      
      <a href="/search/?searchtype=author&amp;query=Liu%2C+Q">Qinging Liu</a>, 
      
      <a href="/search/?searchtype=author&amp;query=Peng%2C+H">Hongyun Peng</a>, 
      
