        Low differentially uniform permutations from Dobbertin APN function over $\mathbb{F}_{2^n}$
      
    </p>
    <p class="authors">
      <span class="has-text-black-bis has-text-weight-semibold">Authors:</span>
      
      <a href="/search/?searchtype=author&amp;query=Wang%2C+Y">Yan-Ping Wang</a>, 
      
      <a href="/search/?searchtype=author&amp;query=Zhang%2C+W">WeiGuo Zhang</a>, 
      
      <a href="/search/?searchtype=author&amp;query=Zha%2C+Z">Zhengbang Zha</a>
      
